will be between $2^{28}$ and $2^{30}$, so that there will be hardly
any loss of accuracy. Then |x| and~|y| are divided by~|r|.

@d forty_five_deg 0264000000 /* $45\cdot2^{20}$, represents $45^\circ$ */
